
Ranger Help for: enemy pig
==========================

SUMMARY:
Choosing pig means your Ranger specializes against boars, swine, hogs,
and tusked rooting beasts.

This is a solid choice for forests, jungles, hills, mountains, and arctic
lands where aggressive boars or pig-like creatures appear.

COMMAND:
  setenemy pig

=============================================================================
SEE ALSO: enemy, setenemy and terrains
